  "texts": [
    "In our work, the adopted CLK is 50 MHz, and the switching time of PIN diode is about 2.5 us each cycle.",
    "Each metasurface panel is equipped with eight 8-bit shift registers (SN74LV595APW), and groups of 8 PIN diodes share the same shift register.",
    "We remark that the proposed control strategy can be readily extended to more PIN diodes by concatenating more metasurface panels, allowing adjustable rearrangement of metasurface panels to meet various needs.",
    "The 5.5 GHz meta-atom has the same structure as the 2.4 GHz except that it scaled down in size.",
    "The 9.7 GHz meta-atom has three substrate layers: the top substrate is Taconic TLX-8 with a relative permittivity of 2.55, and the middle and bottom substrates are FR4."
